Education and Labor; Veterans' Affairs; elected to the 115th Congress on 
November 8, 2016; reelected to each succeeding Congress.

JONI ERNST, Republican, of Red Oak, IA; born in Red Oak, July 1,
1970; education: graduated Stanton High School, Stanton, IA; B.S., Iowa 
